(436, 17, 2, '2015-05-08', '2015-05-11 13:51:01', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7321482'']: ''[UPD2][ANMP][180][2.5.5]Gift received pop-up: Back key has no functions =&gt;&nbsp;dispatchClick("btnAccept") in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - PopupsHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7323960'']: ''[UPD2][ANMP][2.5.7]Change name pop-up: Back key has wrong function =&gt;&nbsp;dispatchClick("btnClose") in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() -&nbsp;PopupsHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7501995'']: ''[iOS][UPD3][ANMP][Controller]MM: The mapping of the AUT buttons isn''t working as intended =&gt; set&nbsp;heightlight on processKeyRelease() -&nbsp;HomeScreenHandler.as</p>'),
(437, 33, 2, '2015-05-08', '2015-05-08 11:26:58', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7477862'']: ''[UPD3][ANMP][Compat]AP: There are many blinking trash pixel on the gun of MC</p>\r\n<p>- We are using&nbsp;EPF_DEPTH24 to draw</p>\r\n<p>- Use&nbsp;isForceClearBuffers() method to force setDepthRange again</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(438, 44, 2, '2015-05-08', '2015-05-08 17:22:08', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7056222'']: ''[UPD1][ANMP][167][3.1.17]All: An error message appears in more than 15 seconds</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Login time out is 70s.</li>\r\n<li>Check if the connection time is greater than 15s. If yes =&gt; show popup</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>- Fixing bug: virtual keyboard always show numberic keyboard</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Added keyboard type from flash -&gt; C -&gt; java</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(439, 5, 2, '2015-05-08', '2015-05-08 20:37:43', '<p>- Update &amp; merge iOS rev 102872 : Done (Lock trunk rev 102892)</p>\r\n<p><strong>- i9500(ID:203604) loading too long (<a href="https://qadb.gameloft.org/Qa/Bugs/View/7075922" target="_blank">7075922</a>) : WIP</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Loading from MM to game (Touch to continue) :&nbsp;212992ms (~3.5min)</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/MobileOptimisation.html">http://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/MobileOptimisation.html</a>&nbsp;:&nbsp;ImgTec PowerVR SGX. Tile based, deferred: render everything in tiles, shade only visible pixels.&nbsp;\r\n<p>This means:</p>\r\n<p>Mipmaps are not so necessary.<br />Antialiasing and aniso are cheap enough, not needed on iPad 3 in some cases</p>\r\n<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: medium;">Name: <strong>createMaterialRenderer</strong> : take too much time</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: medium;">[MC5] reference from Fran&ccedil;ois Duranleau&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
