(541, 43, 2, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 11:17:10', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7507824'']: ''[UPD3][ANMP][G+]Change Name: The user''s name change back to the G+ name after relaunch AUT</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Crash x86 (Memo Pad 204550+ 204567)</p>\r\n<p>- Build so + no installer:</p>\r\n<p>- Build so + has installer :</p>\r\n<p>- Build so_x86 + has installer : crash data (Age screen)</p>\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Build so_x86 + no&nbsp;installer :</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7315830'']: ''[UPD2][ANMP][CRM][4.4.11] Pop up is not alignment in center</p>\r\n<p>-&gt; InitializePopupsLib() - PopupsLib.cpp</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>public int getStatusBarHeight() {<br />int height = 0;<br />int resourceId = getResources().getIdentifier(&ldquo;status_bar_height&rdquo;, &ldquo;dimen&rdquo;, &ldquo;android&rdquo;);<br />if (resourceId &gt; 0) {<br />height = getResources().getDimensionPixelSize(resourceId);<br />}</p>\r\n<p>return height;<br />}</p>'),
(542, 17, 2, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 18:15:54', '<p>! Waiting for IOS check bug:&nbsp;7525879 - Loading screen: NVS appears in first loading screens. Because IOS changed flow of age popup to affect NVS popup flow.</p>\r\n<p>! Waiting for IOS can enter the game to check some bugs sound.</p>'),
(543, 13, 3, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 20:59:37', '<p>[''7516884'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP] Team: The long user name is spilled out of the avatar box.</p>\r\n<p>[''7518623'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][LOC][AS][ML]Introduction: Text in page 3 overlaps and flickers</p>\r\n<p>[''7508844'']: ''[UPD14] Tournament Result screen:The unicorns are overlap the lines when multitask to other screens.</p>\r\n<p>[''7516748'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP]Team Uno:The create game and the team uno tabs stick to top screen buttons</p>\r\n<p>[''7521077'']: ''[UPD14][TOK][GP][Maga event/item doubler]: Font size of texts "Cost real money" is too small.</p>\r\n<p>[''7514266'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][COPPA][Restore save]WA: Restore save prompt appears again after select G+ save files.</p>\r\n<p>[''7524567'']: ''[iOS][UPD14][COPPA] WA: The Restore Saves prompt is still displayed after restoring a save.</p>\r\n<p>[''7525997'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][COPPA]Restore save prompt: Age gate appear again after select None button.</p>\r\n<p>[''7507306'']: ''[UDP14][ANMP][2.14.3]Team: The Bounce-Back Effect is implemented in this section</p>\r\n<p>[''7511302'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP]Team Uno: The select tier section is hard to scroll</p>\r\n<p>- Status: Fixed</p>'),
(544, 15, 3, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 16:50:27', '<p>* [''7521155'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][Age gate] Age gate appears after user disconnected from SNS</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;- Status:&nbsp;Done</p>\r\n<p>* [''7527229'']: ''[UPD14][TOK][GP][About]: Tester''s name is incorrect</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;- Status: Inprogress</p>'),
(545, 16, 3, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 20:43:51', '<p>[''7524581'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP]Result screen: Game crashes when user taps to "New Game"</p>\r\n<p>[''7524417'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][2.5.5] Option: Back key has no function in Option</p>\r\n<p>[''7525085'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][Controller] Scratch screen: AUT crashes after go back to main menu</p>\r\n<p>[''7525111'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][Controller] Scratch screen: The share pop-up can not be reached using controller</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;-Status: Done</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(546, 7, 4, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 17:06:16', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7525515'']: ''[UPD24][ANMP][14.1.16]The AUT does not respect the intended behavior when TC is added in new version</p>\r\n<p>- Implement setBaseUrl for InGameBrowser (updated at ACP r12633) - DONE</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7531008'']: ''[UPD24][ANMP][AMAZ][2.26.8]NVS: New language TC isn''t localized in NVS pop-up with AUT''s language</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7498147'']: ''[UPD24][ANMP][LOC][MS][TC]MM: Text do not localize in Server News and Update Notes section</p>'),
(547, 40, 2, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 11:51:17', '<ul>\r\n<li>Merge server</li>\r\n<li>Debug TLE</li>\r\n<li>Merge CRM</li>\r\n<li>Update-&gt;clean all source -&gt; rebuild source (try to solve unstopable crash when update source last time)</li>\r\n</ul>'),
