(549, 14, 3, '2015-05-19', '2015-05-19 19:04:30', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7527917'']: ''[UPD14][TOK][GP][IAP]: Error message that Google Play Store is old version is appeared once</p>\r\n<p>- updated IAP lib to lastest revision<br />- mail to support team</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7514826'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP][Compat] Loading screen: All text becomes trash pixel&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- CNR in v240d</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7054938'']: ''[UPD11][ANMP][Compat][MM] there are black trash pixel around fake WS</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7484094'']: ''[UPD14][ANMP]Dare: The dare avatars are missing in some screens<br />- fixed</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
