(664, 5, 2, '2015-06-02', '2015-06-02 20:01:01', '<p>- IAP restore : WIP</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>[IAP][MC5_UPD3] Issue with IAP restore&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>In the InAppBilling log the items is not recognized as non consumable,&nbsp; in your game object that the managed items are set correctly</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/17804095/in-app-billing-v3-android-non-consumable-items">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/17804095/in-app-billing-v3-android-non-consumable-items</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://developer.android.com/google/play/billing/api.html">http://developer.android.com/google/play/billing/api.html</a></li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>- MEMO crash : CNR&nbsp;</p>'),
(665, 17, 2, '2015-06-02', '2015-06-02 18:25:15', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7571952'']: ''[UPD3][ANMP][2.5.5]Events / Leaderboard / More reward: Back key has no function =&gt;</p>\r\n<p>1/ Link "POPUP_EVENT_REWARDS" to "PopupsHandler" in Controller.as.</p>\r\n<p>2/ Set back key for "POPUP_EVENT_REWARDS" in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - PopupHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7572374'']: ''[UPD3][ANMP][2.5.5]Deploy/deploying screens: Back button has no function =&gt;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1/ Set back key in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - KillCamHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>2/ Set back key in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - PauseMultiplayerHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7544444'']: ''[UPD3][TOK][GP][MP][Clan battle]: Clan name text is overlapped when waiting for other clan member =&gt; set position of "logo" in&nbsp;squadLogo() &amp;&nbsp;setBackground() - SquadLabel.as</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(666, 16, 3, '2015-06-02', '2015-06-02 11:53:45', '<p>[''7572722'']: ''[UPD14][AMAZ][T]:Parameter social_network registered as 0 instead of 113420</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;-Status: Done</p>\r\n<p>[''7560302'']: ''[UPD14][AMZ][T]: Event CRM Cross Promo Install not registered on ODD2.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;- Status: CNR</p>'),
