(668, 17, 2, '2015-06-03', '2015-06-03 16:07:06', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7572432'']: ''[UPD3][ANMP][MP] Device''s Back key doesn''t have function on Result screen =&gt;</p>\r\n<p>1/ Link "MENU_MISSION_OUTCOME_MULTIPLAYER_SOLO" to "MissionOutcomeHandler" in getSubjectHandlerClass() - Controller.as.</p>\r\n<p>2/ Set back key for "name_btnExit" in processKeyRelease() - MissionOutcomeHandler.as</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7561472'']: ''[UPD3][ANMP]MM/Supply Packs: Some killsign is missed image in "Possible Winnings" box =&gt; Missing some code in PackOffer.as.</p>'),
