(688, 17, 2, '2015-06-11', '2015-06-11 16:30:47', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7605710'']: ''[UPD3][TV]MM: The mapping of the AUT buttons isn''t working as intended =&gt; change highlight in processKeyRelease() - HomeScreenHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7605658'']: ''[UPD3][TV] Black Market: The user can not move highlight anywhere except the Buy button =&gt;</p>\r\n<p>1/ Set name for button "Info" in BlackMarket.as.</p>\r\n<p>2/ Set highlight for "BlackMarket" menu in BlackMarketHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7606200'']: ''[UPD3][TV][12.10.10]WA: The 5% safe zone contains texts and graphics of HUD.</p>'),
(689, 5, 2, '2015-06-12', '2015-06-12 08:56:16', '<p>- Support DLC issue for MC5 MEX (Pub version) : DLC''s OK now , only device(GPU) issue</p>\r\n<p>- Clone and checkout UPD4 : WIP</p>\r\n<p>- Checking bugbase status</p>'),
(690, 17, 2, '2015-06-15', '2015-06-15 15:22:31', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7605756'']: ''[UPD3][TV]Battle Packs: The user can''t move highlight to "i" button =&gt;</p>\r\n<p>1/ Add name for "info" button in&nbsp;init() - BattlePacks.as.</p>\r\n<p>2/ Set X&nbsp;button to select "info" button in processKeyRelease() - BattlePacksHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7606074'']: ''[UPD3][TV]Energy refill: User can''t move the highlight to x2 token button =&gt; set hightlight for "token" in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - PopupVIPEnergyHandler.as.&nbsp;</p>'),
(691, 40, 2, '2015-06-16', '2015-06-16 11:51:39', '<p>- config Game server 140</p>\r\n<p>- make document</p>\r\n<p>- Study server checksum</p>'),
(692, 17, 2, '2015-06-16', '2015-06-16 16:02:59', '<p><strong>* Bug Fixed [''7605788'']: ''[UPD3][TV]Events Details: The user can not highlight to the More Reward button = &gt; set highlight for "name_btnMoreRewards" button in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() -&nbsp;EventDetailsHandler.as.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>* Bug Fixed [''7622066'']: ''[UPD3][TV]Restore successful pop-up: All button key has no function in this pop-up =&gt; set hightlight for "POPUP_BUNDLES_NOTIFICATION" in&nbsp;reset() - PopupsHandler.as</strong></p>'),
(693, 17, 2, '2015-06-17', '2015-06-17 18:01:24', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7625562'']: ''[UPD3][TV]The Lie/Connect popup: There is no highlight at all =&gt; set default highlight for "connectButtonGplus" if on TV in&nbsp;reset() - PopupHandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7606200'']: ''[UPD3][TV][12.10.10]WA: The 5% safe zone contains texts and graphics of HUD =&gt; add safezone.</p>'),
