(695, 5, 2, '2015-06-18', '2015-06-18 11:09:16', '<p>- Update src for UPD4 :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>LevelFogZ.h:70:12: error: reference to ''CMemoryStream'' is <strong>ambiguous</strong></li>\r\n<li>temp remove code of iOS in UPD3 to fix this : rev 104880&nbsp;- [Android] template fix error: ''CMemoryStream'' has not been declared // revert 6984594</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/15037705/reference-to-function-is-ambiguous">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/15037705/reference-to-function-is-ambiguous</a>&nbsp;:&nbsp;First, <strong>don''t use<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> <code>using namespace</code></span></strong><code> =&gt; Dont add <strong>using namespace</strong> in global (class,...)&nbsp;</code></li>\r\n<li><code>\\OnlineManagers\\SocialLibManager.cpp:1174:6: error: ''GameAPISNSWrapper'' has not been declared =&gt; Only add "using namespace in<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong> each function</strong> </span>need&nbsp;</code></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>- Check bugbase for TV</p>'),
(696, 17, 2, '2015-06-18', '2015-06-18 17:40:56', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7604122'']: ''[UPD3][TV][ANMP][Controller] Friends: User can''t move highlight to CONNECT button of Google+ =&gt; change name of "name_btnGooglePlus" button to "name_btnGooglePlusConnect" in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - Friendhandler.as.</p>\r\n<p>* Bug Fixed [''7622272'']: ''[UPD3][TV]MP/Deploy: User can''t move highlight to VOTE MAP button =&gt; set heighlight in&nbsp;processKeyRelease() - KillCamHandler.as.</p>'),
(697, 17, 2, '2015-06-19', '2015-06-19 17:11:49', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7631586'']: ''[UPD3][TV]Duplicate item found: The controller has no function with this pop-up =&gt;</p>\r\n<p>1/ Link "POPUP_DUPLICATE_ITEM'' to "PopupsHandler" in&nbsp;getSubjectHandlerClass() - Controller.as.</p>\r\n<p>2/ Set heighlight "btnDone" and back key for it in PopupHandler.as.</p>'),
(698, 17, 2, '2015-06-22', '2015-06-22 12:46:30', '<p>* Bug Fixed [''7605948'']: ''[UPD3][TV]Incentivised Videos: The Free Credits text is stuck on screen =&gt; set distance of&nbsp;"freeLabel.textField.y" in&nbsp;syncAlpha() - CreditsButton.as</p>');
